SerialDataExplorer is used to be build andinstalled using the GNU 
standard way  calling 

./configure && make && make install

Since this is a Java based program there are several tools required 
where Java based programs build and execution relies on

	Java SDK
	ant

The default install directory is /opt/SerialDataExplorer
First time startup is required usage of the start script in the
installation director. Afterwards the application gives the 
capability to maintain desktop shortcuts as well as start menu
entries. During runtime online help is available.
